text: Ranggung LRT Station is an LRT station in Sengkang, Singapore. It is part of the Sengkang LRT Line. It is on the east loop. It opened on 18 January 2003. == Name == Ranggungs are storks that live on the Punggol coast. == Timeline == 18 January 2003 - The station opened. == Sources == == Other websites == https://www.sbstransit.com.sg Category:Sengkang Category:Light Rail Transit (Singapore) stations
title: Ranggung LRT Station
